name: Get Dat Money!
description:
Get Dat Money!

Story

Times running out, but you're a tycoon and know how to get your money. Go!

How to Play

Your goal is to pick up as many cash bundles as you can before time runs out.

*Sound Included

Controls

 Arrow Keys or W-A-S-D for movement

Credits
